{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, it is also important to resort to more low-cost LLMs such as Vicuna [58] for helping embodied agents in the future.",
    "Landmark cooccurrence extraction.To verify the superiority of LLM in landmark cooccurrence extraction, we present the comparison of obtaining landmark cooccurrences between ChatGPT and ConceptNet in Fig. 8.",
    "To get the cooccurrences of a target landmark through ConceptNet, we respectively request its related terms and nodes which are connected with relations of 'AtLocation' and 'LocatedNear'.",
    "From Fig. 8 we can observe that LLM can generate visible cooccurrences as constrained in the prompt (Sec.",
    "D.1) which are informative and high-quality."
  ]
}